SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT CLNT205_EMP_CONTACT, CLNT101_ADMNO,CLNT102_CLNTNO, CLNT103_COMM_ADMNO, CLNT103_COMM_CLNTNO, CLNT110_NAME1, CMON_CURRBALFACTACC, CMON_CURRBALSPECIALACC, CMON_CURRBALSETTLEMENTACC, CLNT108_ACC_CURR
FROM :1 cross join :6 LEFT OUTER JOIN :2 ON (CMON_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO AND CMON_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO AND CMON_YEAR = :3 AND CMON_MONTH = :4 AND CMON_CURRENCY = CLNT108_ACC_CURR)
WHERE :5
FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS
